quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  18,1,"[All] praise is [due] to Allāh, who has sent down upon His Servant [Muḥammad (ﷺ)] the Book and has not made therein any deviance.<sup foot_note=196691>1</sup>",footnotes:196691:1
  18,2,"[He has made it] straight, to warn of severe punishment from Him and to give good tidings to the believers who do righteous deeds that they will have a good reward [i.e., Paradise]."
  18,3,"In which they will remain forever"
  18,4,"And to warn those who say, "Allāh has taken a son"."